  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8290052">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8290052/" class="title-link">国家历史文化延续的点灯人</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8290052"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/cgnlml/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u139582526-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cgnlml/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">春城邂逅</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-01-13"
      class="main-meta">2017-01-13 13:07:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8290052_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  电视剧《搭错车》主题曲《酒干倘卖无》从同事的小音箱传到我的耳膜里。让人思绪飘飞，先是想到搭错车中收破烂的佟林，再想到近两天看的电视剧《正阳门下》收破烂的韩春明，做文物高仿品的程建军。《我在故宫修文物》中的主角具有程建军的高超技术，不过没有程建军的“坏心思”...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8290052/#comments">(14回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">27有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8290052_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8290052_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8384945">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8384945/" class="title-link">故宫深处的“扫地神僧”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8384945"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/149447792/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u149447792-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/149447792/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">雾凇</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-02-26"
